# I have successfully moved to the iron patch. 
# Now, I will attempt to harvest iron ore from this location.

# I will aim to gather a quantity of 20 iron ore from the patch.
harvested_iron = harvest_resource(iron_position, quantity=20)
print(f'Attempting to harvest {harvested_iron} iron ore from the patch.')

# After harvesting, I will check my inventory to confirm the increase in iron ore.
print(f"Updated inventory: {inspect_inventory()}")
